            "title": "日股全程報升 收漲0.6%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">日股全日報升，日經平均指數在全日低位58687點時仍升逾200點；指數收報58824點，升348點或0.6%。</p>\n</div>",
